name: Cryostasis 008
description:
'Cryostasis 008' is part of a series of images exploring alien landscapes and other-worldly dimensions. Each image is computer generated and taken through a multi-layered production process to create the final image. This includes the initial render, then compositing and 
 editing using various render passes, and finally retouching to produce the final result.

Limited to only 10 editions.
